            <title>[LU-2401] Add ability for lu_key to be allocated upon first get but not during initialization.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2401</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This idea arose during llog_thread_info implementation. Often such thread info may not be ever used. The generic mechanism is needed to don&apos;t allocate keys if they are might be not needed, but do that upon first get that key.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
